review: The Eiffel Tower at night is breathtaking!
Loved exploring the small cafes and museums in Paris.
Tokyo’s cherry blossoms are a must-see!
The sushi in Tokyo is out of this world.
New York’s skyline is unlike any other.
Broadway shows were the highlight of my trip!
The pyramids are a wonder of the world for a reason.
Cairo’s history is fascinating, but it can get very hot!
Sydney’s harbor is stunning, and the Opera House tour is great.
Bondi Beach is perfect for surfing!
